{"ProductId":"380","Title":"Bridgeport™ Inlay","ShortDescription":"Clean, simple recessed panel design combined with classic carriage house detailing","Description":"","ThumbnailImage":null,"ShowcaseImage":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/bpinlayshowcase01.webp?sfvrsn=96c68ec5_4","CanonicalUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/bridgeport-inlay","Overview":"<h3>Versatile Design Meets Durability</h3><h4>Textured Details That Pop</h4><p>A pebbled texture on the Inlay highlights its character, blending effortlessly with woodgrain and stucco textures for a look that&rsquo;s both subtle and unique.</p><h4>Built for Versatility</h4><p>Available in one-, two- or three-layer construction on <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/Bridgeport\">Bridgeport&trade; extended panels</a>, with your choice of 7', 7'3\" or 8' heights and 21\" or 24\" section sizes, so you can find the right fit for any opening.</p><h4>Designs That Speak to You</h4><p>Choose from three eye-catching carriage house inlay patterns&mdash;A, X, or V&mdash;to create exactly the look you want. Finish it off with one of ten solid color options featuring a woodgrain-embossed steel surface, or go with an <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/ultra-grain\">Ultra-Grain&reg; finish</a>. Premium Black and Iron Ore finishes include thicker 25-gauge steel plus solar reflective paint.</p><h4>Tough Outside, Cozy Inside</h4><p>The durable fiberglass inlay combats harsh weather and UV rays on the exterior. Inside the door, you can choose <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/residential/buyingguide/intellicore\">Intellicore&reg; polyurethane insulation</a> for exceptional warmth and strength or opt for efficient polystyrene. With R-values ranging from 6.3 to 18.4, you can select the balance of comfort, energy savings, and affordability that works best for your home.</p><h4>Make It Yours</h4><p>You can customize the door with one of six glass options: clear, frosted, midnight gray, seeded, rain, and obscure. Each one lets in a degree of natural light, privacy, and adds a unique touch of style.</p><h4>Ready for Harsh Conditions</h4><p>Add <a href=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/buyingguide/residential/windcode-residential-information\">WindCode&reg; reinforcement </a> (up to W8 on select models) for additional strength and reliability when the weather turns rough.</p><h4>Environmental Assurance</h4><p>Clopay doors are compliant with environmental laws and regulations. Clopay doors do not contain HFCs. All Clopay doors are compliant with:</p><ul><li>California SB 1013</li><li>Washington HB 1112 &ndash; Hydrofluorocarbon Greenhouse Gas Emissions</li><li>Canadian regulations amending the ozone-depleting substances and halocarbon alternatives regulations</li><li>New Jersey A-5583/S-3919 &ndash; Greenhouse Gas Bill</li></ul>","Options":"","Construction":"<h3>How It&rsquo;s Made: Bridgeport&trade; Inlay</h3><p>Every Bridgeport&trade; Inlay garage door starts with a durable core. Select from one-, two- or three-layer construction on sturdy extended panels designed to handle the demands of everyday life. The Inlay is crafted from tough fiberglass that resists warping, weather, and UV light, keeping your door looking its best year-round.</p><p>The Inlay features a pebbled texture that pairs well with woodgrain or stucco surfaces, layered over a steel base and finished with woodgrain embossing. You can choose a solid color or if you prefer the Ultra-Grain&reg; finish, you can select from one of four warm tones&mdash;Medium Oak, Dark Oak, Walnut Oak or Slate Oak. The premium Black and Iron Ore options have a thicker 25-gauge steel with advanced solar reflective paint for extra durability and style.</p><p>Each door is made with galvanized steel and a protective metal oxide layer, then finished with a durable primer and a baked-on topcoat that stands up to rain, sun, and snow. Complete your design with one of three carriage house patterns (A, X, or V) and your pick of six glass styles.</p><p>Every door comes with a replaceable bottom seal to keep out dirt and drafts, plus hardware and steel hinges for quiet, reliable operation. For extra protection in harsh weather, choose WindCode&reg; reinforcement up to W8 on select models.</p><p><img sf-image-responsive=\"true\" src=\"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/construction/inlaycutaway.webp?sfvrsn=d6ca65bc_2\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;\" title=\"inlaycutaway\" alt=\"Bridgeport Inlay cutaway\" sf-size=\"7304\" /></p><ol><li>Steel</li><li>Intellicore&reg; Polyurethane or Polystyrene Insulation</li><li>Steel</li></ol>","Models":"","FeaturesBenefits":"","SpringsHardware":"","GroupName":"","H1HeaderTitle":"Bridgeport Inlay","DisplayIndex":12,"ImageGallery":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/image-gallery/bridgeport-inlay","ColorDisclaimer":"<p>Finding your perfect color is easy. Go classic with ten solid shades, including White, Almond, Desert Tan, Sandtone, Chocolate, Mocha Brown, Bronze, and Charcoal. You can also choose from four warm Ultra-Grain&reg; options. If you want to make a statement, Black and Iron Ore are also available, both built with a thicker steel skin and advanced solar reflective paint.</p><p>Keep in mind: some premium finishes are available only on select door models, so check which colors fit your design.</p><p>(S) Stucco Texture<br />(W) Woodgrain Texture<br /></p><p><em>*Not available on all models<br /></em></p><p><em>Black and Iron Ore are subject to additional fee and only available on 25-gauge steel<br />Exterior steel on standard color doors has a natural woodgrain texture.<br />Doors can be painted to match the home&rsquo;s exterior using a high-quality\r\n        latex exterior paint. Do not use oil-based paint.</em></p>","TopSectionDisclaimer":"<p>You can also personalize your Bridgeport&trade; Inlay door with window (or no window) options tailored to your taste. Go with a solid top section for a clean, cohesive look, or let in some light with your pick of six glass options: clear, frosted, midnight gray, rain, seeded, or obscure. Clear glass creates an open feel, frosted and obscure block the view while keeping the garage bright, and rain or seeded glass add decorative texture. Midnight gray delivers a sleek, dramatic tint. Whether you want full visibility and brightness or a touch of privacy, there&rsquo;s a glass style to match.</p><p><em>*Acrylic window designs.<br />Note for Double Top Sections: These are specific to double car doors, in addition to options above.</em></p>","HardwareDisclaimer":"<p>Round out your design with hardware that ties everything together. Every Bridgeport&trade; Inlay door comes with color-matched lift handles. You can take it up a notch by adding decorative handles and hinges in spade, spear, or colonial styles, all built to coordinate with your finish. You can even add matching step plates or twisted &ldquo;T&rdquo; or &ldquo;L&rdquo; handles, each option giving your door a bit more personality.</p>","DesignDisclaimer":"<p>Depending on door height, exact door appearance and number of sections may be different than illustrations above.&nbsp;<a data-sf-ec-immutable=\"\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://clopaypdfs.com/pdf_files/RSDR-RESISTACKGUIDE-20.pdf\">Click here</a>&nbsp;for complete details.</p>","RelatedProducts":[{"Title":"Gallery<sup class='symbolstxt'>®</sup> Steel","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/gallery-steel-ug-long-rec14-595.webp?sfvrsn=a7ceae04_9","Id":"12","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/gallerysteel","DisplayIndex":8,"ShortDescription":"Grooved panel steel carriage house garage doors","AlternativeText":"Gallery Steel"},{"Title":"Bridgeport™ Steel","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/product-images/showcase-images/bridgeport-595.webp?sfvrsn=22fc6bb4_12","Id":"250","Url":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/bridgeport","DisplayIndex":11,"ShortDescription":"Timeless recessed panel style in durable, modern steel","AlternativeText":"Bridgeport Steel"}],"ProductBrochures":[{"Title":"Bridgeport™ Inlay Brochure","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/rsdr-bridgeportinlayss-26-1.webp?sfvrsn=36a46ea1_3","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-BRIDGEPORTINLAYSS-26.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":1},{"Title":"Ultra-Grain Paint Option Brochure","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/rsdr-ultragrain-08.webp?sfvrsn=af90ad27_4","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-ULTRAGRAIN-08.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":2},{"Title":"Products Available Through Independent Dealers","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/brochures/idea-book.webp?sfvrsn=699cfb64_5","Type":"Brochure","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/RSDR-IMAGINE-14.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":3}],"ProductInstallationAndCare":[{"Title":"Steel Garage Doors Care and Maintenance","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/care-and-maintenance/steelgaragedoors.webp?sfvrsn=deb8b1e_3","Type":"Finish & Care","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/CMB-4150089_EN.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":1},{"Title":"Installation Manual for Residential Sectional Insulated Steel Doors","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/installation-instructions/installmanual-insulatedresi.webp?sfvrsn=15f3a601_3","Type":"Instruction Manual","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/INST-4150077_EN.pdf","Extension":"PDF","DisplayIndex":2},{"Title":"Residential Sectional 1-Layer And 2-Layer Doors","ImageUrl":"https://www.clopaydoor.com/images/default-source/installation-instructions/installmanual-1-2-layer.webp?sfvrsn=2a3599a4_2","Type":"Instruction Manual","Url":"https://literature.clopay.com/pdf_files/INST-4150078_EN.pdf","Extension":"PD